I"*	<p>09/2016 – 02/2017 @ Anglia Ruskin University</p>

<p>The module allowed students to create original music and sound design for poetry, short films and games by using acoustic and computer-based methods of composition. It provided networking and career opportunities. Please see <a href="/">index page</a> for more recent teaching resources.
<br /></p>

